content: The total manufacturing pipeline for SG Developing Corp projects is estimated to approximately be $800 million based on current analysis, we estimate the manufacturing margin to be approximately 15% on an open book basis. In the coming weeks and months, we will deliver additional detail on the develop of our Sanitec partnership, we are very excited about the future of SG Development Corp as we've seen the first developments break ground over the last quarter, and we're continuously looking for opportunistic movements to go forward in these projects alone to keep our factories full for years to come.
